{"type": "article", "id": 35502, "title": "这盏吊灯，用 64 个框架玩光影的游戏｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-12T23:10:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26280, "name": "Odesi"}, {"id": 35727, "name": "Michael Raymond"}, {"id": 35733, "name": "Alex Groot Jebbink"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 143, "image": "img/article/article_show/201612122101476X0xsZ8BOCG5jnfY.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Glint Side Table by Michael Raymond</h3><p>英国设计师 <a href=\"https://michaelraymond.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michael Raymond</a> 2007 年毕业于考文垂大学工业设计系，并于去年成立了自己的家具和灯具品牌，这张名为 Glint 的边桌是旗下的第一款产品。充满了金属光泽、宛如镜面的边桌由 95% 的回收不锈钢制作而成，也体现了 Raymond 的环保意识。桌子的一端还附带了一个收纳桶，可以放上香槟或是花束。这是它的<a href=\"https://michaelraymond.com/shop/glint-side-table-mirrored-stainless-steel\" rel=\"nofollow\">订购链接</a>，售价为 5000 英镑。</p><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172222gQNCTW14REmx3Vph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172222ekzZ2jr4qF8WpsAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172222mYInNLAGgxPBraHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172222LPEiVQoABIsvetbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172222athcpRdIxYvKHsy4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Embrace by Madhu Priyanka Kannabiran</h3><p></p><p>经历了办公室中 9 到 13 个小时的久坐之后，空闲时间里为什么不多换几个姿势坐着呢？印度设计学生 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Madhu_Kannabiran\" rel=\"nofollow\">Madhu Priyanka Kannabiran</a> 的作品 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45994753/Embrace-A-Renaissance-in-chairs\" rel=\"nofollow\">Embrace</a> 就是这么一把有着极高灵活度的椅子。虽然没有传统的椅腿或是座位，你依然可以借助圆球和两边的绑带随心所欲地休息，将它环绕在身边时的确会有一种被拥抱的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612121722112TVsfWdh5mCyvBSA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172211sEL47wmaODnxZWKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612121722111V9hldouqsPN7mQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172212UI6DJMHQ054bpAR3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172212HlCFsvB9OPRK2fkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Angles by Alex Groot Jebbink</h3><p>荷兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.a-lex.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alex Groot Jebbink</a> 最近为家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.odesi.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Odesi</a> 设计了一款富有立体感的吊灯 Angles，不同角度吊起时会呈现出字母 X 或是十字形状。实际上它的结构并不复杂，Jebbink 用激光切割技术将 64 张中密度纤维板（MDF）打造成了大小各异的长方体框架，最后再把它们组合在一起就呈现出了这个奇特的效果。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.odesi.eu/designer-pendant-light-angles\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1125 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212205724YxDwFR2083SjX4Va.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212205724pScbg3njlZ61ImCF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212205724rJH7Ly8uma5fZxYP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212205724w5tEFaComBRcJYMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612122057241fpMicblAgom0aEL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.329630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>+Winter by +t team</h3><p>大冬天手脚冰冷总是难捱，在没有供暖设备加持的地方，一双厚袜子或许也并不能彻底解决问题。为了让更多人不再脚底冰凉，来自瑞士的 +t 设计团队研发了一款加热鞋垫 +Winter，它的大小和普通鞋垫无异，前、后端的厚度仅为 2 和 6 毫米。使用前需要将鞋垫放在专用的充电器上充电，放入鞋子后就可以通过配套的应用通过手机激活，甚至可以通过它为两个鞋垫分别设定加热温度，最长可使用 5 小时。去年这款鞋垫在去年底就已经在欧洲集资成功并出货了，团队最近又启动了一次范围更广的众筹，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1929258659/winter-ultra-thin-wireless-charging-heating-insole\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与，早鸟价为 99 瑞士法郎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172102n5NfDR3oyvE4HMkq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172102zGy3h1ULdY8pe5fm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172103eGo6OHSidwBINM84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.316176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612121721037fK6as9JwLhSjD8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.973529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172102gw1jhY9aRT47bAe0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.408824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Instasnap by Johandré Saayman</h3><p>不想随身携带手机又希望能在社交网站上随时分享自己的生活？来自南非的工业设计学生 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Johandre\" rel=\"nofollow\">Johandré Saayman</a> 以 Instagram 为设计灵感带来了这款概念相机 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46012737/Instasnap-dedicated-Instagram-social-media-camera\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instasnap</a>，主打易操作和便携两大特点。它的机壳会让人想起 App 的旧版 logo，机身只有三个按键：顶部的按钮既是开关又是快门，一侧的两个按钮则是用来在选项界面进行设置的。从 Saayman 构想的配置来看，这个可以在水下 10 米使用的迷你相机的确很适合在不方便使用手机的场合使用，不知未来是否有产品化的可能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212182209KCmnrypogqjcleGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212182208acbsJ5nPjp7X01TD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212182208o2HjvDG4hsI3C7BN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212182208BgcDbhjPT5GVSRxm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.618095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212182209Z3ScV2K7UApJrkbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rice Packaging by Jamie Alloy</h3><p>就读于美国泰勒艺术学院（Tyler School of Art）的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/JamieAlloyDesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jamie Alloy</a> 带来了一套赏心悦目的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46177129/Rice-Packaging\" rel=\"nofollow\">大米包装</a>。纸包装的两侧敞开可以让顾客直观地确认大米的质量，正反两面布满了 Alloy 根据大米产地的文化特色所设计的一套图案，有着恰到好处的异域感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172154ySaXb9M2wlDomWV5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172155oZlkNDYLfOXtjGmP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161212172159RBJqQrp1oPxtYh5v.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}